{"tid":1723844,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"屌奶星 幫襯間黃店食咗小妹500蚊","createTime":"2019-11-15T09:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T06:49:50.000Z","uid":14090,"like":8,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8440be4adddedaf6bae4834c47a22c5453d20409","tid":1723844,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:54:24.000Z","msg":"小妹今日心情曳無食lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁tea time有啲肚餓豬咪搵間黃店食個tea<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到間黃店本身乜事都冇既 小妹心情都好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知仆你個街 隔離枱班牙叔開口埋口又暴徒 又暴動 又話支持警甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小妹心情又曳返 屌你老味我拎堆cash出嚟 派一人一張一百蚊比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同佢地講：唔係要你改變你立場 屌你老母可唔可以比我靜靜地食餐飯 張單我埋 屌你老母出返去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我啲朋友話我益咗班藍絲 小妹心諗 是撚但啦 反正小妹大把錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時捐比星火都幾千幾千咁捐啦 五舊水收買到藍絲 睇下幾撚無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b646893f977a167773bfcce80e50cbd083b7db1a","tid":1723844,"uid":261873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"我係藍絲<br />\n派埋畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40986a60ce26784f9c9e81870ba932348803e704","tid":1723844,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b646893f977a167773bfcce80e50cbd083b7db1a","tid":1723844,"uid":261873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"我係藍絲<br />\n派埋畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:55:50.000Z","msg":"等本小姐有心情先"},{"pid":"a7c5b5fc27df85cfbc0f1621995981a64e70d4e9","tid":1723844,"uid":14090,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:56: